lled it out before I hit the ball.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not even a perception; it's the rules.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always have to advocate for myself.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"JUST IN:'Disqualify them' - Olympic officials told to boot Rafael Nadal and Carlos Alcaraz out of doubles drawShe also said: \\\"It always happens here at the French Open to me.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every time.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is like the fourth, fifth time it's happened this year.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Gauff was asked about the incident after her defeat.But the 20-year-old insisted she would not blame the row with Campistol for the disappointing result, saying: \\\"I am not going to sit here and say one point affected the result today, I was already on the losing side of things.READ MORE:England add another name to next manager shortlist as three 'favourites' emerge to replace Gareth Southgate\\\"I felt that he called it before I hit, and I do not think the ref disagreed.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\